title: Carter's: Babies are Made to Love | Little Layette
description:
From tiny hands and feet to big smiles and hugs, this aww-inspiring video has it all while introducing Carter's 2015 Little Layette collection. These new baby clothes feature cute new colors, pretty prints and bold stripes that are great for easy mix & match outfits. 

Made to love since 1865, you can count on Carter’s for everything you need to keep your baby clothed in comfort and swaddled in style.
